#
# 0001 ngsi services
#
ngsi services

```
NAME:
   ngsi services - manage services for IoT Agent

USAGE:
   ngsi services command [command options] [arguments...]

COMMANDS:
   list     list configuration group
   create   create a configuration group
   update   update a configuration group
   delete   remove a configuration group
   help, h  Shows a list of commands or help for one command

OPTIONS:
   --host value, -h value     host or alias
   --token value              oauth token
   --service value, -s value  FIWARE Service
   --path value, -p value     FIWARE ServicePath
   --help                     show help (default: false)
   --version, -v              print the version (default: false)
   
```

#
# 0002 ngsi devices
#
ngsi devices

```
NAME:
   ngsi devices - manage devices for IoT Agent

USAGE:
   ngsi devices command [command options] [arguments...]

COMMANDS:
   list     list all devices
   create   create a device
   get      get a device
   update   update a device
   delete   delete a device
   help, h  Shows a list of commands or help for one command

OPTIONS:
   --host value, -h value     host or alias
   --token value              oauth token
   --service value, -s value  FIWARE Service
   --path value, -p value     FIWARE ServicePath
   --help                     show help (default: false)
   --version, -v              print the version (default: false)
   
```

